距离任仅有数天的时任[[美国总统|美国总统]][[乔治·沃克·布什|乔治·沃克·布什]]致电萨伦伯格来感谢他拯救了乘客的生命<ref name=GWB>{{cite news| title = Bush salutes Hudson River pilot who landed plane| publisher = [[美联社|美联社]]| date = 2009-01-16| url = http://www.google.com/hostednews/ap/article/ALeqM5gzMdsFeJ5wmBEPLUTBjxw_VRVFagD95ODEK80| accessdate = 2009-01-16| archive-date = 2009-01-21| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090121183714/http://www.google.com/hostednews/ap/article/ALeqM5gzMdsFeJ5wmBEPLUTBjxw_VRVFagD95ODEK80| dead-url = no}}</ref>，当时的[[美国总统当选人|当选美国总统]][[贝拉克·奥巴马|贝拉克·奥巴马]]也致电来邀请萨伦伯格以及全体机组人员参加[[2009年美國總統就職典禮|2009年美國總統就職典禮]]<ref name=Guardian_20090119>{{cite news| title = Obama, Sullenberger invitation to inauguration| work = [[衛報|衛報]]| first = Robert| last = Booth| date = January 19, 2009| url = http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2009/jan/19/obama-honours-martin-luther-king| accessdate = 2009-01-19| archive-date = 2012-10-15| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121015180537/http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2009/jan/19/obama-honours-martin-luther-king| dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news| title = Obama, Sullenberger speak by phone| publisher = [[CNN|CNN]]| date = January 16, 2009| url = http://politicalticker.blogs.cnn.com/2009/01/16/obama-sullenberger-speak-by-phone/| accessdate = 2009-01-16| archive-date = 2020-08-17| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200817125720/https://politicalticker.blogs.cnn.com/2009/01/16/obama-sullenberger-speak-by-phone/| dead-url = no}}</ref>。2009年1月16日，[[美国参议院|美国参议院]]通过了一份决议来表彰萨伦伯格、副机长杰夫·斯基尔斯、客舱乘务员多琳·威尔士（Doreen Welsh）、希拉·戴尔（Sheila Dail）和唐娜·登特（Donna Dent）、乘客和急救人员<ref>{{cite web| title = Text of S.Res.17 Recognizing and honoring Captain Chesley `Sully' Sullenberger III, his co-pilot Jeffrey Skiles, the crewmembers of U.S. Airways Flight 1549, and the first responders, ferry operators| publisher = Library of Congress| date = 2009-01-16| url = http://www.thomas.gov/cgi-bin/query/z?c111:S.+Res.+17:| accessdate = 2009-01-31}}{{Dead link|date=2020年7月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。1月26日，[[美国众议院|美国众议院]]通过了一份相似的决议以赞许其表现<ref>{{cite web| title = Text of H.Res.84 Honoring the heroic actions of the pilot, crew, and rescuers of US Airways Flight 1549| publisher = Library of Congress| date = 2009-01-26| url = http://thomas.loc.gov/cgi-bin/query/z?c111:H.RES.84.ATH:| accessdate = 2015-06-13| archive-date = 2016-01-26| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160126174602/http://thomas.loc.gov/cgi-bin/query/z?c111:H.RES.84.ATH:| dead-url = no}}</ref>。

他被{{link-en|英国航空联盟|The Air League}}授予奠基者奖章<ref name=Airleague>{{cite web|title=Sully receives UK air league medal from duke of edinburgh|url=http://www.flightglobal.com/news/articles/sully-receives-uk-air-league-medal-from-duke-of-edinburgh-327561/|publisher=Flightglobal|accessdate=2015-05-23|archive-date=2019-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191206085502/https://www.flightglobal.com/news/articles/sully-receives-uk-air-league-medal-from-duke-of-edinburgh-327561/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。1月22日，他和全美航空1549号班机机组的其余人员被{{link-en|飞行员与领航员行业协会|Guild of Air Pilots and Air Navigators}}授予大师奖章<ref name=Masters>{{cite web|url=http://www.flightglobal.com/blogs/flight-international/2009/11/capt-sullenberger-awarded-gapa/|title=Capt Sullenberger awarded GAPAN Master's Medal|publisher=Flightglobal|author=Barbara Cockburn|date=2009-11-03|accessdate=2015-06-10|archive-date=2015-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150610212013/http://www.flightglobal.com/blogs/flight-international/2009/11/capt-sullenberger-awarded-gapa/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。1月24日，[[丹维尔_(加利福尼亚州)|丹维尔]]为萨伦伯格举行了一个典礼，他在典礼上也被授予包括丹维尔“城镇钥匙”在内的奖项<ref name=MacAskill_Guardian_20090126/>。他也被授予丹维尔荣誉警员的称号<ref>{{cite news| title = "Just doing my job" says hero pilot Chesley Sullenberger| publisher = [[泰晤士报|泰晤士报]]|first=Philippe|last=Naughton| date = January 25, 2009| url = http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/news/world/us_and_americas/article5583941.ece| accessdate = 2009-01-29 |location=London}}</ref>。他被授予{{tsl|en|Seaplane Pilots Association|水上飛機飛行員協會}}终身荣誉会员<ref>{{cite news| title = 1549's Sullenberger Becomes Honorary Policeman And Seaplane Society Member| publisher = AVweb| date = January 24, 2009| url = http://www.avweb.com/avwebflash/news/SullenbergerEarnsAccolades_199650-1.html?CMP=OTC-RSS| accessdate = 2009-01-29| archive-date = 2016-10-01| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161001192917/http://www.avweb.com/avwebflash/news/SullenbergerEarnsAccolades_199650-1.html?CMP=OTC-RSS| dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news| title = SPA and Jack Brown's Seaplane Base Honor Heroic Water Landing| publisher = Seaplane Pilot's Association| date = January 19, 2009| url = https://www.seaplanes.org/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=617&Itemid=46| accessdate = 2009-01-29| deadurl = yes| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160308025624/http://seaplanes.org/index.php?id=617&itemid=46&option=com_content&task=view| archivedate = 2016-03-08}}</ref>。7月，他回到了他的母校美国空军学院，并获颁了{{link-en|贾巴拉飞行技术奖|Jabara Award}}，观看了阅兵以及被安排飞了一次滑翔机<ref>{{cite web|title=Hero Capt. Sully Lands Air Force Award|url=http://www.nbcwashington.com/news/archive/NATLHero-Capt-Sully-Lands-Air-Force-Award.html|publisher=NBCwashington|accessdate=2015-05-08|language=en|date=2009-07-13|archive-date=2019-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191206141933/https://www.nbcwashington.com/news/archive/NATLHero-Capt-Sully-Lands-Air-Force-Award.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。9月，他与斯基尔斯一起出任EAA计划的副主席<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.aviationpros.com/press_release/10397872/eaa-names-sullenberger-and-skiles-new-young-eagles-chairmen|title=EAA Names Sullenberger and Skiles New Young Eagles Chairmen|work=AviationPros.com|accessdate=2015-06-12}}</ref>。在2010年11月，萨伦伯格被授予[[法國榮譽軍團勳章|法國榮譽軍團勳章]]<ref>[http://www.gettyimages.com/detail/news-photo/airways-capt-chesley-sully-sullenberger-at-the-presentation-news-photo/114425193 "The French Legion Of Honor Presents Chesley Sullenberger With The Officier Award"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.gettyimages.com/detail/news-photo/airways-capt-chesley-sully-sullenberger-at-the-presentation-news-photo/114425193 |date=20200730172422 }}. [[盖帝图像|盖帝图像]]. December 17, 2010.</ref><ref>[http://news.speedtv.com/photo/02x2dtF7Ui1Jz?q=Chesley+Sullenberger "The French Legion of Honor Presents Chesley Sullenberger With The Officer Award"] {{Wayback|url=http://news.speedtv.com/photo/02x2dtF7Ui1Jz?q=Chesley+Sullenberger |date=20130602134635 }}. [[Speed_(TV_channel)|Speed]]. December 17, 2010.</ref>。

2009年2月1日，萨伦伯格夫妇一同当次班机其他机组，受[[国家美式足球联盟|国家美式足球联盟]]邀请参加[[第四十三届超级盃|第四十三届超级盃]]赛前庆祝仪式<ref>{{cite news| title = Super ovation for 'Sully', US Airways crew| publisher = NBC Sports| agency = Associated Press| date = February 1, 2009| url = http://nbcsports.msnbc.com/id/28967586/| accessdate = 2009-02-01| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090203143717/http://nbcsports.msnbc.com/id/28967586/| archive-date = 2009-02-03| dead-url = yes}}</ref>。萨伦伯格为[[舊金山巨人|舊金山巨人]]掷出了[[美国职业棒球大联盟|美国职棒]]2009赛季的{{link-en|首掷|First Pitch}}。他的运动衫的号码是155号，象征着1549号航班上的155人<ref name="Giants">{{cite web|url=http://www.mercurynews.com/peninsula/ci_12095405|title=Mountain View school reunion at Giants' opener|last=Reid|first=John|date=April 7, 2009|work=Mercury News|accessdate=2009-04-14|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303202904/http://www.mercurynews.com/peninsula/ci_12095405|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他后来也为[[奥克兰运动家|奥克兰运动家]]和[[纽约洋基|纽约洋基]]投了开赛球，他也在2009年7月14日在[[圣路易斯_(密苏里州)|圣路易斯]]参加[[2009年美国职棒大联盟全明星赛|2009年美国职棒大联盟全明星赛]]开赛之前的红毯走秀。他被选为于[[帕萨迪纳_(加利福尼亚州)|帕萨迪纳]]举行的2010年[[帕萨迪纳_(加利福尼亚州)|帕萨迪纳]][[玫瑰花车游行|玫瑰花车游行]]的{{link-en|游行大礼官|Grand Marshal}}<ref>[http://www.google.com/hostednews/ap/article/ALeqM5hyFRaMyNYacAJ3fnMkx-5922G62wD9BPMPB80 Splashdown pilot Sullenberger to lead Rose Parade], ''Associated Press'', November 5, 2009</ref>。

2009年1月24日，萨伦伯格在美国众议院公共交通和基础设施委员会的航空小组委员会上作证，指出他的薪水被缩减了四成，他的退休金同大部分航空公司的退休金计划一样被替换为几乎不值钱的{{link-en|养老金待遇担保公司|PBGC}}的担保<ref>[http://www.gpo.gov/fdsys/pkg/CHRG-111hhrg47866/pdf/CHRG-111hhrg47866.pdf ''US Airways Flight 1549 Accident'', Hearing] {{Wayback|url=http://www.gpo.gov/fdsys/pkg/CHRG-111hhrg47866/pdf/CHRG-111hhrg47866.pdf |date=20170310125306 }}. February 24, 2009. U.S. House, Subcommittee on Aviation, Committee on Transportation and Infrastructure. . Washington: Government Printing Office, 2009.</ref>。萨伦伯格做出警告称航空公司正在采取紧缩政策，迫于压力不得不招募缺乏经验的飞行员，有经验的驾驶员拒绝如此低薪的工作，部分运输公司甚至雇佣只有数百小时经验的飞行员。他还强调“在保障航空安全上，没有什么可以轻易替代经验。”<ref name="syracuse.com">{{cite web|url=http://www.syracuse.com/news/index.ssf/2010/03/miracle_on_the_hudson_pilot_ch.html|title='Miracle on the Hudson' pilot Chesley Sullenberger retires|work=syracuse.com|accessdate=24 May 2015|archive-date=2018-09-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180927005715/https://www.syracuse.com/news/index.ssf/2010/03/miracle_on_the_hudson_pilot_ch.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==退役后生活==
[[File:Sullenberger_Sydney.JPG|thumb]]
在为全美航空及其前身工作30年后，萨伦伯格于2010年3月3日退役。他执飞的最后一班航班是全美航空1167号班机，从佛罗里达的[[劳德代尔堡|劳德代尔堡]]起飞前往北卡羅來納州的[[夏洛特_(北卡羅來納州)|夏洛特]]。他与当年同他操纵飞机迫降哈德逊河的副机长杰夫·斯基尔斯驾驶，机上还有6名当年的乘客<ref name="syracuse.com"/>。萨伦伯格表示他对航空安全的倡导和飞行的热爱将会一直延续下去<ref name=Bomkamp/>。

2010年12月，萨伦伯格被授予法国国家荣誉军团军官勋位<ref>{{Cite web|title=US Airways Capt. Chesley "Sully" Sullenberger at the presentation of...|url=https://www.gettyimages.com/detail/news-photo/airways-capt-chesley-sully-sullenberger-at-the-presentation-news-photo/114425193|access-date=2021-12-11|work=Getty Images|language=en-us}}</ref>。

同时，萨伦伯格也继续演讲生涯，时常在各种教育机构、企业、与非营利组织举办的论坛上讨论例如航空安全、高性能系统改进、领导力文化、风险和危机管理等话题。2011年，他在[[达沃斯论坛|达沃斯世界经济论坛]]与瑞士经济论坛上发表了演讲。

2011年11月18日， 作为一个资金筹集计划的一部分，萨伦伯格飞往位于夏洛特的{{link-en|卡罗来纳州航天博物馆|Carolinas Aviation Museum}}，当年上演哈德逊河奇迹的空巴A320在那里展出，他也在事故后第一次进入飞机<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.charlotteobserver.com/2011/11/18/2786400/sully-reunited-with-miracle-plane.html |title=Sully reunited with 'miracle' plane |last=Washburn |first=Mark |work=The Charlotte Observer |date=2011-11-19 |accessdate=2011-11-19 }}{{dead link|date=2017年11月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。

萨伦伯格在退役后作了多次关于机遇挑战和团队合作等话题的演讲<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.washingtonspeakers.com/speakers/speaker.cfm?SpeakerID=6592|title=Chesley B. (Sully) Sullenberger, III|publisher=|accessdate=24 May 2015|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150421035048/http://www.washingtonspeakers.com/speakers/speaker.cfm?SpeakerID=6592|archivedate=2015年4月21日}}</ref>，包括2010年7月在[[狮子会|狮子会]]国际年度会议上演讲，称自己只是“非常状况下的普通人”<ref>{{cite web|url=http://m.smh.com.au/lifestyle/celebrity/ordinary-sully--tells-lions-of-his-extraordinary-day-20100702-zsda.html|title='Ordinary' Sully  tells Lions of his extraordinary day|publisher=|accessdate=24 May 2015|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304190906/http://m.smh.com.au/lifestyle/celebrity/ordinary-sully--tells-lions-of-his-extraordinary-day-20100702-zsda.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。以及在2011年的[[世界经济论坛|世界经济论坛]]上力劝政治和商界领导要注重长远的利益<ref>{{cite web|url=http://blogs.reuters.com/davos/2011/01/26/hudson-pilot-tells-business-leaders-to-look-beyond-short-term/|title=Hudson pilot tells business leaders to look beyond short-term|work=Reuters|accessdate=24 May 2015|archive-date=2019-09-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190911144406/http://blogs.reuters.com/davos/2011/01/26/hudson-pilot-tells-business-leaders-to-look-beyond-short-term/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

萨伦伯格在事故后撰写的回忆录《{{link-en|最高职责|Highest Duty: My Search for What Really Matters}}》登上了[[紐約時報暢銷書榜|紐約時報暢銷書榜]]，这本书后来被翻译成中文发售<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ebeijing.gov.cn/BeijingInformation/BeijingNewsUpdate/t1197205.htm|title='Highest Duty' translation team meets press - eBeijing.gov.cn|publisher=|accessdate=24 May 2015|archive-date=2019-09-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190914122111/http://www.ebeijing.gov.cn/BeijingInformation/BeijingNewsUpdate/t1197205.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。萨伦伯格撰写的第二本书是《做出改变：美国领导人勇气和眼界的故事》（''Making a Difference: Stories of Vision and Courage from America's Leaders''），内容有关领导能力，于2012年5月15日发售。

[[CBS新聞|CBS新聞]]以航空和飞安专家的名义雇佣了萨伦伯格<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.charlotteobserver.com/2011/06/01/2343060/hero-pilot-sullenberger-lands.html#storylink=misearch|title=Hero pilot Sullenberger lands new job at CBS News|last=Bauder|first=David|work=[[美联社|美联社]]|date=2011-06-02|accessdate=2011-06-15}}{{dead link|date=2017年11月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。萨伦伯格在电视节目中发表了自己对包括[[马来西亚航空370号班机空难|马来西亚航空370号班机空难]]和[[德国之翼航空9525号班机空难|德国之翼航空9525号班机空难]]在内的飞行事故的看法<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-26572575|title=Flight MH370: Pilot Sullenberger on emergency priorities|work=BBC News|accessdate=24 May 2015|archive-date=2014-06-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140604110658/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-26572575|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cbsnews.com/news/germanwings-crash-sullenberger-us-safeguards-pilot-health/|title=Sullenberger: U.S. has safeguards in place for pilot health|date=29 March 2015|publisher=|accessdate=24 May 2015|archive-date=2019-12-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191204134133/https://www.cbsnews.com/news/germanwings-crash-sullenberger-us-safeguards-pilot-health/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==个人生活==
萨伦伯格与健康专家以及电视明星蘿琳·“罗莉”·萨伦伯格结婚（Lorraine "Lorrie" Sullenberger）<ref name=MSNBC/>，他们有两个养女<ref name=Telegraph>{{cite news| last = Moore| first = Matthew| title = New York plane crash pilot Chesley B. Sullenberger III: Committed to air safety| work = [[每日电讯报|The Telegraph]]| date = January 16, 2009| url = http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/northamerica/usa/4250935/New-York-plane-crash-pilot-Chesley-B.-Sullenberger-III-Committed-to-air-safety.html| accessdate = 2009-01-16| archive-date = 2020-11-28| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201128115147/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/northamerica/usa/4250935/New-York-plane-crash-pilot-Chesley-B.-Sullenberger-III-Committed-to-air-safety.html| dead-url = no}}</ref>，凯特（Kate）和凯莉（Kelly）<ref name=MercuryNews>{{cite web| last = Kazmi| first = Sophia| title = Wife of Danville pilot says 'This is the Sully I know'| work = San Jose Mercury News| date = January 16, 2009| url = http://nl.newsbank.com/nl-search/we/Archives?p_product=SJ&p_theme=sj&p_action=search&p_maxdocs=200&s_dispstring=headline,lead(experienced%20pilot)%20AND%20date(1/14/2009%20to%201/16/2009)&p_field_date-0=YMD_date&p_params_date-0=date:B,E&p_text_date-0=1/14/2009%20to%201/16/2009)&p_field_advanced-0=title&p_text_advanced-0=(%22experienced%20pilot%22%29&p_bool_advanced-1=OR&p_field_advanced-1=Lead&p_text_advanced-1=(%22experienced%20pilot%22%29&xcal_numdocs=20&p_perpage=10&p_sort=YMD_date:D&xcal_useweights=no| accessdate = 2009-08-19| archive-date = 2020-10-06| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201006102759/http://nl.newsbank.com/nl-search/we/Archives?p_product=SJ&p_theme=sj&p_action=search&p_maxdocs=200&s_dispstring=headline%2Clead%28experienced%20pilot%29%20AND%20date%281%2F14%2F2009%20to%201%2F16%2F2009%29&p_field_date-0=YMD_date&p_params_date-0=date%3AB%2CE&p_text_date-0=1%2F14%2F2009%20to%201%2F16%2F2009%29&p_field_advanced-0=title&p_text_advanced-0=%28%22experienced%20pilot%22%29&p_bool_advanced-1=OR&p_field_advanced-1=Lead&p_text_advanced-1=%28%22experienced%20pilot%22%29&xcal_numdocs=20&p_perpage=10&p_sort=YMD_date%3AD&xcal_useweights=no| dead-url = no}}</ref>。萨伦伯格一家定居在加利福尼亚州[[丹维尔_(加利福尼亚州)|丹维尔]]<ref name=MercuryNews/><ref>Branch, Kirsten (September 27, 2010).[http://danville.patch.com/articles/cityread-2010-features-captain-sully-sullenbergers-book-highest-duty "CityRead 2010 Features Capt. 'Sully' Sullenberger's Book, 'Highest Duty'"] {{Wayback|url=http://danville.patch.com/articles/cityread-2010-features-captain-sully-sullenbergers-book-highest-duty |date=20120618070150 }}. Patch Media.</ref>。他是一名跑步爱好者<ref>{{cite web |title= I'm a Runner: "Sully" Sullenberger |url= http://www.runnersworld.com/celebrity-runners/im-runner-sully-sullenberger |date= 2012-09-04 |accessdate= 2015-06-09 |archive-date= 2015-05-11 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20150511035432/http://www.runnersworld.com/celebrity-runners/im-runner-sully-sullenberger |dead-url= no }}</ref>。他没有支持某个政党的意愿<ref name=Wilson>{{cite news| last = Wilson| first = Reid| title = GOP tried to recruit hero pilot 'Sully' for 2010 Congress bid| work = ''The Hill''| date = 2009-10-01| url = http://thehill.com/homenews/campaign/61179-gop-recruited-hero-captain-sully-for-2010-congress-run-| accessdate = 2009-10-05| archive-date = 2020-12-05| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201205165801/https://thehill.com/homenews/campaign/61179-gop-recruited-hero-captain-sully-for-2010-congress-run-| dead-url = no}}</ref>。

萨伦伯格积极参与志愿事业，他是美国[[红十字会|红十字会]]的支持者<ref>{{cite web|url= https://www.linkedin.com/in/sullysullenberger |title=capt. sully sullenberger|publisher=linken in|accessdate=2015-05-24}}</ref>，在2010年他作为{{link-en|圣裘德儿童研究医院|St. Jude Children's Research Hospital}}的代言人参与了一档电视广告的录制<ref>[http://www.stjude.org/stjude/v/index.jsp?vgnextoid=0e32cc9e0a9c3210VgnVCM1000001e0215acRCRD&vgnextchannel=5f24598943c8d110VgnVCM1000001e0215acRCRD&SearchUrl=search_results.jsp&QueryText=Sullenberger "A hero among heroes"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.stjude.org/stjude/v/index.jsp?vgnextoid=0e32cc9e0a9c3210VgnVCM1000001e0215acRCRD&vgnextchannel=5f24598943c8d110VgnVCM1000001e0215acRCRD&SearchUrl=search_results.jsp&QueryText=Sullenberger |date=20120308072130 }}, St. Jude Children's Research Hospital, accessed December 24, 2010.</ref>。

==流行文化==
滑稽演员、电台主持人{{link-en|加里森·凯勒|Garrison Keillor}}为2009年播出的喜剧《[[牧场之家好做伴|牧场之家好做伴]]》写了一首《飞行员之歌：给切斯利·萨伦伯格三世的民谣》（Pilot Song: The Ballad of Chesley Sullenberger III）。2011年音乐团体{{link-en|College (音乐团体)|College (musical project)|College}}的歌曲《真正的英雄》（A Real Hero）被选作电影《[[亡命驾驶|亡命驾驶]]》的片尾曲，歌词中有提到萨伦伯格和1549号航班的内容<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/drive-soundtrack-captain-sully-254349 |title= 'Drive' Song Inspired by Captain Sully Sullenberger and 'Mad Max' |author= by Michael O'Connell |publisher= Hollywoodreporter |date= 2011-10-27 |accessdate= 2015-06-12 |archive-date= 2020-11-09 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20201109031629/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/drive-soundtrack-captain-sully-254349 |dead-url= no }}</ref>。

萨伦伯格在2012年1月8日播出的的《[[特工老爹|特工老爹]]》“不勇敢的那一个”一集中展现了他充满活力的一面<ref>{{cite episode|title=The Unbrave One|series=[[特工老爹|特工老爹]]|season=7|episode=8|network=[[福克斯廣播公司|福克斯廣播公司]]|airdate=January 8, 2012}}</ref>。

一种[[鸡尾酒|鸡尾酒]]被命名为“萨利”（Sully）来表达对萨伦伯格的敬意，一杯“萨利”包括两小杯{{link-en|灰雁 (伏特加)|Grey Goose (vodka)|灰雁伏特加}}和一些水<ref>{{cite web |url=http://aviationblog.dallasnews.com/2009/02/a-cocktail-named-after-sully-s.html |title=A cocktail named after Sully Sullenberger? |author=Terry Maxon |work=Dallas Morning News Aviation Blog |date=2009-02-01 |accessdate=2014-12-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150309190640/http://aviationblog.dallasnews.com/2009/02/a-cocktail-named-after-sully-s.html/ |archive-date=2015-03-09 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

在2011年3月14日首播的航空事故纪录片《[[空中浩劫|空中浩劫]]》里他由演员{{link-en|克里斯·布里顿|Christopher Britton (actor)}}在情景重建中扮演<ref>{{cite episode|series=[[空中浩劫|空中浩劫]]|title=Hudson River Runway|season=10|number=5|network=[[探索頻道|探索頻道]]|airdate=March 14, 2011}}</ref>。

2015年，导演[[克林特·伊斯特伍德|克林特·伊斯特伍德]]围绕萨伦伯格当年的水上迫降拍摄了电影《[[薩利機長：哈德遜奇蹟|薩利機長：哈德遜奇蹟]]》<ref name=film/>，于2016年9月2日在北美上映。萨伦伯格机长由[[汤姆·汉克斯|汤姆·汉克斯]]扮演<ref>{{cite news|title=航空電影「薩利機長：哈德遜奇蹟」到底有多真實？|url=http://solomo.xinmedia.com/air/89608-sully|publisher=欣傳媒|date=2016-08-31|accessdate=2016-09-11|archive-date=2019-12-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191205203051/https://solomo.xinmedia.com/air/89608-sully|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

